# Invariants & contracts
  @invariant  channels are 1..16 internally; +1 applied on read from REAPER, -1 on write  @ 2
  @invariant  loc is 1-indexed REAPER event-order; not stable across reloads  @ 3
  @invariant  mm holds realisation frame; delay baked into note-on ppq (docs/timing.md)  @ 4
  @invariant  mm holds raw pb; cents/detune + absorber pb live in tm (docs/tuning.md)  @ 5
  @invariant  muted is true-or-absent; false coerces to nil at write; pass false to clear  @ 6
  @invariant  per-event metadata persists via eventMeta, keyed by the take's POOL guid (docs/eventMeta.md)  @ 7
  @invariant  note.chan ∈ 1..16; pitch/vel ∈ 0..127; muted is true-or-absent  @ 494
  @invariant  a plain cc has no sidecar in the take; its uuid is in-memory only, re-minted every load  @ 496
  @invariant  cc.evType ∈ {cc, pb, pa, at, pc}; pa stores in .vel, others in .val  @ 497
  @invariant  cc.cc set on evType='cc'; cc.pitch set on 'pa'; chan ∈ 1..16; cc/pitch ∈ 0..127  @ 498
  @invariant  cc.shape ∈ {step, linear, slow, fast-start, fast-end, bezier}; tension only on bezier  @ 499
  @contract  load is always external (lock-free): reads the take, normalises in-memory, reprojects  @ 514
  @contract  dedup/unify/reconcile mutate the model + set dirty; flushTake writes once if dirty  @ 515
  @contract  a take still holding loadedBlob is converged: fires reload{wholesale=false, chans={}}, returns  @ 516
  @contract  metadata persists incrementally: reassignment clones out, uuids no event claims swept  @ 517
  @contract  stage-3 consensus: winning offset needs ≥ max(2, ceil(0.5·n)) votes, unique  @ 686
  @contract  load fires signals in order: takeSwapped, notesDeduped, uuidsReassigned  @ 818
  @contract  then: ccsDeduped, ccsReconciled, collisionsResolved, reload, flushed (iff wrote)  @ 819
  @contract  dedup/reconcile signals fire only when their event kind has ≥1 record  @ 820
  @contract  holds the nest open across the caller's modifies; takes no lock, writes nothing  @ 967
  @contract  not a gesture -- fires no reload, and an error propagates rather than printing  @ 968

